Package meico.supplementary

Some data structures and functionality that is useful across the different data types.
Author:
Axel Berndt
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ColorCoding
    This class interfaces a color coding scheme to be used, e.g., in spectrograms.
    KeyValue<K,V>
    A helper class for key value pairings, used in class AccentuationPatternDef, and all the ...Map classes.
    RandomNumberProvider
    This class provides random numbers based on the specified distribution.
